OL,5, The UK's public debt could soar as the 
OL,6, population ages and tax receipts fall, 
OL,7, the government's independent forecaster
OL,8, has warned.                            
OL,10,FThe Office for Budget Responsibility   
OL,11,Fsaid debt could rise to more than 300% 
OL,12,Fof the size of the economy by 2070, up 
OL,13,Ffrom around 100% currently.            
OL,15,FClimate change and geopolitical        
OL,16,Ftensions also posed "significant" risks
OL,17,Fto government finances, it added.      
OL,19,FBut it called current government plans 
OL,20,Fto reduce debt "relatively modest".    
